</div>
<div class="faq-wrapper">
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What types of packaging do you specialize in?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>We craft everything from luxury rigid boxes and elegant mailers to eco-friendly kraft packaging. Our 30+ categories cover beauty, food, retail, gifts, electronics, and specialty items.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How does the Custom Design Service work?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Simply fill out our design request form with your brand details, style preferences, and requirements. Our expert designers will create 2-3 custom mockups within 24-48 hours completely FREE with your order!</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do you ship internationally?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely! We deliver worldwide including USA, Canada, UK, Europe, Australia, and beyond. Shipping is complimentary on all orders.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Is there a minimum order requirement?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Zero minimums! Whether you need 10 boxes or 10,000, we treat every order with the same premium care and attention.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does production take?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Standard production runs 8-10 business days from design approval. Rush orders available for urgent needs.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What materials do you use?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>We use premium eco-friendly materials including FSC-certified paper, recyclable cardboard, kraft, and biodegradable options. All materials meet international quality standards.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I request samples before ordering?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes! We offer sample kits so you can feel the quality firsthand. Contact us to request samples with your specific requirements.</p></div></div>
<div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What are your payment terms?<span class="faq-toggle"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></span></div><div class="faq-answer"><p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, Amex), PayPal, Stripe, and wire transfers. Custom payment plans available for bulk orders.</p></div></div>
</div>
